<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>转向；求助于：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Their talk turned to the change that had taken place in the city. 
他们的话题转到了城市发生的变化。</p></div>

